leadingComments.value:
*
 * Create an Array by duplicating values 
 * 
 * @param {Array} s size of the Matrix
 * @param {Array} v value
 * @returns {Array}
 * @example
 * 
 * rep([2,3], 0)
 * // [[0,0,0],
 *     [0,0,0]] 
 * 
 * rep([3], 5)
 * // [5,5,5]
